{
  "series": {
    "title": "The Covenant Chronicles",
    "tagline": "Wanted For Nothing",
    "bio": "A masked vigilante and his Covenant answer theft and murder with fire. They protect their own — and the Crows never stay dead.",
    "preface": "In the ruins of the survivor settlements, fourteen million was stolen from a green leaf and its courier left for dead. M125CC found him — and Covenant answered.\n\nWhat began as one act of vengeance became a war. The Crows of the SHAT faction were wiped from the map, yet they always came back: mocking the armor, planting bombs, daring Covenant to respond. M125CC leads with rage. Fitz keeps the balance. Sym pulls the strings. One leads, one balances, one plans — together, Covenant stands.\n\nStronghold by stronghold, bomb by bomb, they protect their own and destroy what threatens them. Now SHAT is scattered — leadership missing, territory gone — but the scattering was only phase one.\n\nCovenant never forgets. Covenant never forgives."
